{"tid":1925914,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"點解台灣有唐鳳、有陳時中，但我地得班撚樣做官？","createTime":"2020-03-14T17:55:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-15T04:26:59.000Z","uid":3513,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"ff92936e3ce017ceee9309eafa43fe87bebfbd3e","tid":1925914,"uid":3513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T17:55:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/oCEG5VfblFg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FoCEG5VfblFg&d=mMkNc61%2FAm5nYK%2BypTXmCWHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=468443b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/oCEG5VfblFg</a><br />\n人地醫護寫封聯署信話N95唔啱帶 人哋陳時中會識得即刻回應再轉買另一隻鴨嘴式N95 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都唔好講陳時中撐起成個防疫擔子做得妥妥當<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後唐鳳都唔洗講啲咩 個口罩系統寫到尾晒機<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/8ZtUKEAefs0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F8ZtUKEAefs0&d=mMkNc61%2FAm5nYK%2BypTXmCWHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=c9d1a92d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/8ZtUKEAefs0</a><br />\n幾完美都好 短時間再改進個系統<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解香港啲官可以咁閪柒咁撚不堪？<br />\n啲垃圾狗官真係香港之恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n俾人讚感染率低仲夠膽走出去拎光環 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63828b4abb7b771836ee0a5be985a51c60866661","tid":1925914,"uid":62815,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T18:00:07.000Z","msg":"人地係國家"},{"pid":"2db61e20b3b55a330859606d08c2728ea5cf3ac6","tid":1925914,"uid":3513,"like":0,"dislike